 } } \right.$$<br><br>At $$ - 3 \le |x| \le 0,f(|x|) =  - 2$$ not possible.<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow f(|x|) = \left\{ {\matrix{
   { - x - 2,} &amp; { - 3 \le x \le 0}  \cr 
