 } } \right.$$<br><br>$$\therefore$$ $$f'(0) = \mathop {\lim }\limits_{h \to 0} {{f(h) - f(0)} \over h}$$<br><br>$$ = \mathop {\lim }\limits_{h \to 0} {{{h^2}\log h} \over h}$$<br><br>$$ = \mathop {\lim }\limits_{h \to 0} h\log h = 0$$

